Fork of martinpaljak/OpenSC. Builds on OS X 10.8

OpenSC documentation wiki is available online at
	http://www.opensc-project.org/opensc/

Please take a look at the documentation before trying to use OpenSC.

MacOS X build dependencies
- The usual build requirements
  - Command Line Tools for Xcode
  - autoconf, automake, autotools, libtool
- Auxiliary Tools for Xcode
  - For PackageMaker
     - You may need to change the path in MacOSX/build-package.in
